        <embedded/>
        <type name="Integer"/>
        <text>The number of days EDI Data will be kept.  By default this is compared with the creation date
but the following EDI Data types compare it with processedDate:

- CM_EDIDataBooking
- CM_EDIDataCustomStop
- CM_EDIDataOperatorStop
- CM_EDIDataReleaseRequest
</text>
    </PrimAttribute>
