        <embedded/>
        <type name="Boolean"/>
        <text>Keep processed Customs/Operator Stop EDI until expiry.

Basically means they don't get deleted once they are DB Loaded

Also used for CM_EDIDataBooking &amp; CM_EDIDataReleaseRequest though not sure it should be!!!!!</text>
    </PrimAttribute>
